# CSS Conventions

## Architecture

- Section-specific styles go in `assets/section-{name}.css`
- Core styles: `assets/styles.css`, `assets/typography.css`, `assets/template-shopify.css`
- Design tokens are injected into `:root` via adapter snippets (not defined in CSS files directly)
- No Sass/.scss files — only native `.css` or `.css.liquid`

## Token Adapters

IMPORTANT: All design tokens flow through these adapter snippets in `snippets/`. Never redefine these values in CSS — reference them.

| Adapter | Tokens Provided |
|---------|----------------|
| `colors-adapter` | Full color scheme system (40+ tokens per scheme) |
| `typography-adapter` | Font families, sizes, scales, line heights |
| `layout-adapter` | Page width, spacing, grid gaps |
| `radius-variable-adapter` | All border-radius tokens |
| `buttons-adapter` | Button styling tokens |
| `inputs-adapter` | Input field tokens |
| `media-adapter` | Media element tokens |
| `modal-drawer-adapter` | Modal/drawer tokens |
| `product-cards-adapter` | Product card tokens |
| `article-cards-adapter` | Article card tokens |
| `collection-cards-adapter` | Collection card tokens |
| `variant-pills-adapter` | Variant pill tokens |
| `general-js-adapter` | Animation/easing JS config |

## Color Usage

```css
/* Correct — use CSS variables */
color: rgba(var(--color-foreground));
background: rgba(var(--color-accent));
color: color-mix(in srgb, rgba(var(--color-foreground)) 75%, transparent);
border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgba(var(--color-foreground)) 20%, transparent);

/* Wrong — never hardcode */
color: #1e1e1e;
background: #fbbf24;
```

IMPORTANT: Colors are stored as RGB triplets (e.g. `30,30,30`). Always wrap with `rgba()` or use `color-mix()` for opacity.

## Responsive Pattern

Mobile-first with 768px as the primary breakpoint:

```css
.component {
  /* mobile styles (default) */
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .component {
    /* desktop styles */
  }
}

@media (min-width: 1400px) {
  .component {
    /* large desktop styles */
  }
}
```

Full breakpoint set: 576, 740, 768, 992, 1140, 1200, 1400, 1600, 1700, 1800, 1900px.

## Fluid Typography

Use the existing clamp pattern for fluid sizing:

```css
--size: clamp(
  min(var(--pfs-min) * 1rem, var(--pfs-max) * 1rem),
  calc(var(--m) * 100vw + var(--pfs-min) * 1rem - var(--m) * var(--min-viewport) * 1rem),
  max(var(--pfs-max) * 1rem, var(--pfs-min) * 1rem)
);
/* Viewport range: --min-viewport: 40 (400px) to --max-viewport: 120 (1200px) */
```

## Easing

Use named easing variables defined in `styles.css`:

| Variable | Curve |
|----------|-------|
| `--out-soft` | `cubic-bezier(0, 0, .3, 1)` |
| `--spring` | `cubic-bezier(.27, .79, .45, 1.24)` |
| `--out-cubic` | `cubic-bezier(.215, .61, .355, 1)` |
| `--in-out-quart` | `cubic-bezier(.77, 0, .175, 1)` |
| `--out-quart` | `cubic-bezier(.165, .84, .44, 1)` |
| `--in-out-sine` | `cubic-bezier(.445, .05, .55, .95)` |

Common transition patterns:
- Fast: `0.2s ease`
- Medium: `0.3s ease-in-out`
- Signature: `0.5s cubic-bezier(.25,.74,.22,.99)`

## Scrollbar Styling

The theme provides custom scrollbar tokens:

```css
--xo-scrollbar-width: 10px;
--xo-scrollbar-radius: 5px;
--xo-scrollbar-thumb-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgba(var(--color-foreground)) 20%, transparent);
--xo-scrollbar-thumb-color-hover: color-mix(in srgb, rgba(var(--color-foreground)) 40%, transparent);
--xo-scrollbar-track-color: transparent;
```

## Section Padding

Sections receive padding via CSS custom properties set by `section-attr.liquid`:

```css
.xo-section {
  padding-top: var(--pt_dt);
  padding-bottom: var(--pb_dt);
}

@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .xo-section {
    padding-top: var(--pt_mb);
    padding-bottom: var(--pb_mb);
  }
}
```

## Animations and Motion

IMPORTANT: Always wrap entrance animations with reduced-motion media query:

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
  .element {
    animation: fade-up 0.5s var(--out-soft);
  }
}
```

Available keyframe animations: `shimmer`, `zoom-in`, `xo-loader-1/2/3`, `rotateClockwise`, `rotateCounterclockwise`.
